feedbackModal_main_3616215\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104twd1665703108686.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/twd1665703108686.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/twd1665703108686.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"twd1665703108686\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Widget property that defines the target URL of a hyperlink or image in a static server page.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"twd1665703108686__section_vkr_t4h_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173229e50\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"twd1665703108686__p_d109292e1_d109293e1_d109294e1\">Specify a value for this property when defining a\n        hyperlink, either as a hyperlink HTML control (for text links), or as an image HTML control\n        (if you want the image to be a link).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"twd1665703108686__p_d109295e1_d109296e1_d109297e1\">The value of this property is concatenated with the\n        value of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Link Text</span> for text hyperlinks or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Image\n          Source</span> for image links, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Target Window</span>, to provide\n        the contents of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;A HREF&gt;</code> tag in the HTML layout.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"twd1665703108686__p_d109298e1_d109299e1_d109300e1\">Uniface uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span> ProcScript\n        statement to evaluate the contents of this field at run time. Therefore, you can use a field\n        substitution to generate the desired URL. For example, you can enter\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">%%LINKVALUE.MYENT.MYMODEL%%%</code> to use the contents of the LINKVALUE\n        field.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"twd1665703108686__section_mw2_x4h_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173229e83\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"twd1665703108686__ul_mrp_1ph_bxb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xff1719469149188.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xff1719469149188.html\" title=\"This widget defines a hyperlink in a static server page. (To use an image as a hyperlink, use the Image USP widget.)\">Hyperlink</a> (USP)</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ypk1719469595014.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypk1719469595014.html\" title=\"This widget displays an image that can represent a hyperlink, have alternative text, or make use of other features that are not available in the picture control.\">Image</a> (USP)</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmf1665703108475.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Link Text (u_hyperldispl)</a><p>Widget property that defines the visible text of a hyperlink in a static server page.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqu1665703109428.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Target Window (u_target)</a><p>Widget property in a static server page that determines the window into which the linked page is loaded.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/npf1665703108397.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Image Source (u_src)</a><p>Widget property that defines the path and file name of the image to display. This property sets the src attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616215\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616215\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Link Value (u_url) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Widget property that defines the target URL of a hyperlink or image in a static server page. Description Specify a value for this property when defining a hyperlink, either as a hyperlink HTML control (for text links), or as an image HTML control (if you want the image to be a link). The value of this property is concatenated with the value of Link Text for text hyperlinks or Image Source for image links, and Target Window , to provide the contents of the <A HREF> tag in the HTML layout. Uniface uses the = ProcScript statement to evaluate the contents of this field at run time. Therefore, you can use a field substitution to generate the desired URL. For example, you can enter %%LINKVALUE.MYENT.MYMODEL%%% to use the contents of the LINKVALUE field. Applies To Hyperlink (USP) Image (USP) Related Links Link Text (u_hyperldispl) Widget property that defines the visible text of a hyperlink in a static server page. Target Window (u_target) Widget property in a static server page that determines the window into which the linked page is loaded. Image Source (u_src) Widget property that defines the path and file name of the image to display. This property sets the src attribute of the <img> tag in the HTML layout of the static server page. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}